        <text><![CDATA[ <p><b>National Education Security Training Act of 2020 or the NEST Act of 2020</b></p> <p>This bill amends the Internal Revenue Code to allow a $1,500 tax credit for veterans and retired law enforcement officers who are employed part-time by a local law enforcement agency to patrol one or more elementary or secondary schools or institutions of higher education.</p>]]></text>
      </summary>
